#!/usr/bin/env bash

cat <<-EOF

This is quick and dirty crontab format help.
See crontab(5) for more details.

The time and date fields are:

    field           allowed values
    -----           --------------
    minute          0-59
    hour            0-23
    day of month    1-31
    month           1-12    (or names)
    day of week     0-7     (0 or 7 is Sunday, or names)

EOF
